%N A396905 a(n) = number of space diagonals in Johnson solid J_n.
%H A396905 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A396905/b396905.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..92</a> (the full sequence).
%H A396905 Blue, <a href="https://math.stackexchange.com/a/1414108">Number of polyhedron diagonals</a>, Mathematics Stack Exchange, 2015.
