%F A396905 a(n) = A396904(n) - A396906(n).
%F A396905 a(n) = (1/2)*(4 + v*(v-3) - (Sum_{k=3..A394913(n)} A394912(n,k)*(k-1)*(k-2))), where v = A242733(n) (see Mathematics Stack Exchange link).
%t A396905 (4 + #*(#-3) - Sum[(k-1)*(k-2), {k, Map[Length, #2]}])/2 & @@@ Array[PolyhedronData[{"Johnson", #}, {"VertexCount", "FaceIndices"}] &, 92]
